'''Switzerland''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Bern, along with Basel, Geneva, Lausanne, Lucerne, Lugano, and Zurich.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Switzerland; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], [[United Arab Emirates]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019.

